Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.04,0:00:02.65,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Pain that won’t heal
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.65,0:00:04.19,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Sadness you feel
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.19,0:00:06.19,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Scars that just refuse to fade\Nfrom memory
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.19,0:00:09.03,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Sometimes the burden’s too much\Nfor one to bear
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.03,0:00:12.40,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Don’t give up on me,\Nplease don’t turn me away
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.45,0:00:15.19,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.19,0:00:18.32,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I’ll hold your hand in mine
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.70,0:00:25.54,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Will I lose my hold on her someday?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.90,0:00:32.30,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Will her smile fade  In a flood of tears\NOr can I keep the fears at bay?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.43,0:00:37.36,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Echoing, distant voices wither into silence.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.36,0:00:42.08,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But there is one thing that\Nwill never ever age…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.40,0:00:46.82,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,my love for you is timeless
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.82,0:00:48.28,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Pain that won’t heal
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.28,0:00:50.03,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Sadness you feel
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.03,0:00:52.07,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Smiles with hearts’ bitterness replaced
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.07,0:00:53.36,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,“I’ll never smile again”
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.36,0:00:54.61,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,“I’ll never let love in”
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.61,0:00:57.28,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Don’t ever say such things to me
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.28,0:01:00.40,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,A future we cannot see
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.40,0:01:03.36,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,All happenings\NFind meaning in the story
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.36,0:01:07.61,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,In time the clouds will clear away,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.61,0:01:11.51,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,so just stay, please stay with me…\NWhoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.31,0:01:17.38,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Who are we to pass through you?\NWhoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.38,0:01:19.65,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That answer will find you someday
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.53,0:01:49.81,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, everybody…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.80,0:02:27.19,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean,\N“Sorry, everybody”?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.26,0:02:32.18,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You won, you idiot…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.02,0:03:03.42,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.88,0:03:07.48,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks to you,\NKenny had fun fighting!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.16,0:03:12.08,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It was a long time since\NI saw Kenny having so much fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.08,0:03:13.47,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.57,0:03:18.14,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Here we go…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.70,0:03:21.27,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo… If you can, please don’t die.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.96,0:03:25.65,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,And if you can, please play\Nwith Kenny again, will you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.77,0:03:26.85,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Please…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.50,0:03:48.51,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The sounds…have stopped.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.69,0:03:51.01,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think Ichigo is all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.18,0:03:52.47,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,We’ve come this far.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.47,0:03:53.91,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,We have no choice\Nbut to believe in him.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.91,0:03:55.58,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That’s true, but…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.82,0:03:59.04,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,This is no time to get distracted.\NIt’s our turn now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.01,0:04:05.10,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,We’re going to jump across.\NAre you ready, Hana?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.10,0:04:05.68,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.34,0:04:07.15,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Here we go!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.49,0:04:08.62,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I’m counting on you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.63,0:04:23.10,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That was dangerous!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.44,0:04:25.51,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.12,0:04:28.55,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The sounds have stopped…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.47,0:04:31.01,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,And the Spiritual Pressure is gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.26,0:04:33.34,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Both of them…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.19,0:04:35.71,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Which of them died?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.81,0:04:38.76,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I don’t know.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.38,0:04:41.37,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The diffused reflection of\Nthe Sekki-Seki is causing
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.37,0:04:44.53,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,the traces of Spiritual Pressure\Nto be wiped away.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.43,0:04:48.34,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.56,0:04:53.89,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,There should be no good reason…\Nthat blood is spilled for my sake.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.23,0:05:00.74,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Please tell me…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.65,0:05:02.94,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Kaien…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.73,0:05:07.31,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,There now…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.44,0:05:10.94,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That should do it!\NIt should be fine now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.94,0:05:11.93,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Umm…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.93,0:05:12.15,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.36,0:05:14.66,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You tied up my arms, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.66,0:05:17.15,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, sorry ‘bout that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.26,0:05:19.16,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it’s too much trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.16,0:05:21.92,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hana, you can just fly with it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.19,0:05:23.15,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hold it…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.60,0:05:28.30,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it! My arms are going to tear off!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.30,0:05:32.44,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,This is impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.25,0:05:45.56,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, Ichigo. I'm a little late…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.37,0:05:48.30,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You’ve been beat up good.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.08,0:05:52.59,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But with Kenpachi Zaraki as your foe,\Nyou could not have expected less.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.81,0:05:55.26,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Taking him out in the process\Nwas quite an achievement.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.45,0:05:59.02,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But, I must say, you fought well.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.02,0:06:01.68,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You endured well. I am impressed.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.42,0:06:03.50,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Do not worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.41,0:06:05.85,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I will not allow you to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.63,0:06:20.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Where’d you come from…kid?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.19,0:06:24.42,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That’s a sword. Aren’t you scared?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.75,0:06:27.76,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It’s a tool for killing people.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.18,0:06:43.05,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Kid… What’s your name?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.51,0:06:45.59,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You don’t have one?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.50,0:06:47.47,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I don’t, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.89,0:06:52.55,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.27,0:06:55.52,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yachiru…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.69,0:07:01.36,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hurray! Hurray! Kenny’s up!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.74,0:07:03.30,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yahoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.30,0:07:04.72,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What about that guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.72,0:07:05.42,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.88,0:07:09.58,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I called for Unohana.\NShe’ll be here soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.12,0:07:11.55,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What about him?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.66,0:07:15.14,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I don’t know.\NI don’t think he’s dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.74,0:07:17.44,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That’s good…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.84,0:07:20.97,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,This way, I can pay him back.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.68,0:07:23.49,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,There’s nothing to pay him back for.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.49,0:07:26.06,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Sure there is! I lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.06,0:07:27.75,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You didn’t lose, Kenny!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.61,0:07:31.96,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You idiot! What’s with that look\Non your face?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.07,0:07:33.92,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But you didn’t lose!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.92,0:07:37.93,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo said, “Zangetsu and I –\Nthe two of us – are fighting together.”
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.26,0:07:41.84,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It was two against one!\NYou won, Kenny!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.44,0:07:44.21,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Don’t laugh like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.20,0:07:49.80,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Fighting together with\Nyour Zanpaku-to…?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.51,0:07:51.51,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yachiru…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.78,0:07:52.58,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.31,0:07:58.55,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You remember that time\NI gave you your name?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.65,0:08:02.02,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.47,0:08:05.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I even remember how many clouds\Nthere were in the sky!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.58,0:08:08.16,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah… Me, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.03,0:08:14.03,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,K-Kenny…?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.18,0:08:15.31,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Be quiet…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.78,0:08:19.34,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I’d forgotten for a long time…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.85,0:08:22.50,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,How painful it is, having no name.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.85,0:08:28.53,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone else would be called by name,\Nbut I didn’t have one.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.26,0:08:31.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That feeling…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.51,0:08:37.12,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It is read “Yachiru.”\NIt’s the name…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.58,0:08:40.97,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,of the one person I wish to be like.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.25,0:08:44.55,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I’ll give it to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.85,0:08:48.80,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ya…chiru…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.20,0:08:50.67,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I’m Kenpachi.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.88,0:08:52.43,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It’s the name given\Nto the mightiest Soul Reaper
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.43,0:08:54.23,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,in every generation.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.50,0:08:56.77,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I will take that name starting today.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.25,0:09:08.34,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I’ve kept you waiting\Nfor such a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.04,0:09:14.68,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You might think,\N“What the heck, after all these years,”
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.96,0:09:17.43,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,but…do you think\Nyou could tell me now…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.50,0:09:19.90,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,what your name is?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.54,0:09:31.14,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,No good, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.28,0:09:35.45,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I want to get stronger.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.77,0:09:39.07,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I found someone to fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.77,0:09:43.65,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I can get stronger. I want to fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.29,0:09:46.30,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I want to get stronger!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.88,0:09:53.34,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It’s been a long time…\Nsince I’ve felt like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.25,0:09:58.84,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I want to get stronger!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.86,0:10:13.12,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I had no name, and no parents.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.46,0:10:20.45,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Where I was, was North Rukongai,\NArea 79, known as Kusajishi.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.78,0:10:24.63,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I have no memory of\Nseeing anything there,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.63,0:10:25.95,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,other than the color of blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.11,0:10:31.00,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone around me was closer\Nto beast than human.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.44,0:10:35.61,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,A baby like me could have been\Nstomped to death at any time.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.64,0:10:38.90,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Then, you came along.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.46,0:10:41.95,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,From North Rukongai,\NArea 80, Zaraki.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.29,0:10:45.59,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,From the very depths of darkness,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.59,0:10:50.04,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,you carved up my bloody world\Nin an instant,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.04,0:10:53.73,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,and…you gave me a name.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.04,0:11:01.43,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,If you hadn’t appeared,\NI would not be here today.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.00,0:11:08.01,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. Since that day,\Nyou have been my entire world.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.50,0:11:11.70,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You can do it, Kenny…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.17,0:11:14.51,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You are the strongest, Kenny!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.51,0:11:17.53,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,So, let’s get stronger\Nand stronger together!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.85,0:11:18.56,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.54,0:11:20.44,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Kenny?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.85,0:11:22.87,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Kenny…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.62,0:11:24.37,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Kenny…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.34,0:11:35.69,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Kenny!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.88,0:11:47.39,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The Spiritual Pressure\Nhas finally died down.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.96,0:11:55.50,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Still, it sure was something fierce.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.44,0:11:58.07,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What’s wrong with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.12,0:12:02.13,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Your body is trembling.\NHow pathetic!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.13,0:12:05.56,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,W-What?!\NYou’re the one who’s trembling!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.56,0:12:08.25,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What?! What part of me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.73,0:12:12.97,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What’s this? Bird droppings?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.54,0:12:17.41,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey, what’s the matter?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.41,0:12:18.14,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.96,0:12:20.96,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,There you are, damn you…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.11,0:12:22.78,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I won’t let you get away!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.91,0:12:35.36,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ganju, you overdid it.\NThat was mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.36,0:12:39.13,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up! What about you?!\NWhat was that medicine?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.33,0:12:40.67,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,This?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.29,0:12:44.30,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It’s a kind of anesthetic\Ncalled “Shinten.”
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.30,0:12:47.74,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,One drop on the skin of someone\Nwith low Spiritual Pressure
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.74,0:12:50.05,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,will cause him to get dizzy and pass out.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.27,0:12:53.03,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You’ve got some\Nscary stuff there, kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.03,0:12:54.30,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.75,0:12:56.69,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But anyway, let’s hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.69,0:12:57.39,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Oh…?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.40,0:13:03.75,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,So the entrance is the shutter type.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.65,0:13:07.26,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Now the question is,\Nhow do we open it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.26,0:13:08.43,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,No problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.43,0:13:11.00,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What do you have this time?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.36,0:13:13.63,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I borrowed a spare key
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.63,0:13:18.05,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,from the underground water channel\Nstorage room last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.31,0:13:22.58,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey… Is it okay for you to do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.21,0:13:26.01,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It’s probably not okay, but…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.24,0:13:27.91,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But I thought about it last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.07,0:13:31.76,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo is getting\Nall battered up fighting…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.76,0:13:34.76,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,while all I do is keep running away.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.13,0:13:37.01,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It looks pretty bad, I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.89,0:13:39.97,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I want to save Rukia, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.26,0:13:45.34,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,So I decided I’d do all I could\Ntoward that end.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.85,0:13:48.72,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Even if it means\NI will be punished later.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.60,0:13:54.23,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, stealing a key\Nis about all I can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.45,0:13:56.81,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That’s why I’m no good.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.25,0:13:59.18,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,No. I’d say it’s enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.53,0:14:00.18,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.21,0:14:02.53,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What you’ve done…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.86,0:14:07.40,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Man, I tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.40,0:14:11.15,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Everybody’s desperate\Nto save this person.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.15,0:14:14.81,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,This Rukia must be quite a cutie…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.81,0:14:17.09,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Well, uh, it’s not that…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.58,0:14:19.14,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You don’t have to get embarrassed.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.14,0:14:24.10,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Let’s see what she really looks like.\NHey, Rukia!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.53,0:14:31.95,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.43,0:14:37.45,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you?\NIchigo’s…comrade?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.70,0:14:39.65,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It’s me, Rukia!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.97,0:14:42.41,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I’m so glad!\NYou’re all right, aren’t you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.41,0:14:44.10,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You’re…Hanataro!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.43,0:14:45.64,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.77,0:14:48.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,We can talk later.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.29,0:14:51.33,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ganju, let’s hurry and\Nget away from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.25,0:14:57.34,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What’s wrong, Ganju?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.80,0:14:59.34,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The pattern on his clothes…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.44,0:15:02.34,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,the unraveling eddy from heaven…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.58,0:15:04.52,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Are you…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.05,0:15:06.52,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,a member of the Shiba clan?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.52,0:15:09.11,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Oh, do you know each other?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.60,0:15:10.53,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.87,0:15:12.09,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I know her.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.43,0:15:17.27,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,As if I could forget…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.29,0:15:19.80,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,that face…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.95,0:15:23.26,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,She's…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.51,0:15:30.01,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,the Soul Reaper\Nwho killed my brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.92,0:15:40.52,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,W-What are you saying, Ganju?\NRukia wouldn’t…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.84,0:15:44.24,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,My brother’s wounds were from a sword.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.13,0:15:46.72,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,His neck was slashed,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.15,0:15:49.45,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,and he’d been stabbed in the chest.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.22,0:15:55.74,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,If he’d fought with a Hollow,\Nwhy did he die of sword wounds?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.94,0:15:58.73,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,And at that time, she told me…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.73,0:16:00.76,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,that she had killed him!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.89,0:16:02.35,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ganju!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.71,0:16:05.43,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That--that can’t be true!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.43,0:16:07.30,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It’s all right, Hanataro.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.29,0:16:10.92,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,He is correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.92,0:16:12.65,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,R-Rukia?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.10,0:16:14.49,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,A member of the Shiba clan…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.88,0:16:16.96,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,No doubt, it was your elder brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.80,0:16:23.96,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Shiba Kaien…was killed by me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.81,0:16:29.01,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Do as you wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.56,0:16:33.45,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,If I die by your hand,\NI will have no complaints.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.72,0:16:34.76,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.40,0:16:37.35,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Please stop, Ganju!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.35,0:16:39.39,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,We didn’t come here for that,\Ndid we?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.70,0:16:41.64,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Didn’t we come here to save her?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.64,0:16:42.81,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Please, Ganju!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.81,0:16:46.70,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Didn’t Ichigo entrust us\Nwith his determination?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.70,0:16:49.18,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up, will you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.52,0:16:57.03,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,W-What’s with this Spiritual Pressure?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.71,0:17:11.85,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What?! Aizen’s been killed?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.51,0:17:18.87,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,When? By whom? Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.14,0:17:20.37,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,This morning, before dawn.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.14,0:17:20.37,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,This morning, before dawn.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.37,0:17:22.03,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The murderer and motives are, as yet…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.37,0:17:22.03,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The murderer and motives are, as yet…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.03,0:17:23.31,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,unknown!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.03,0:17:23.31,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,unknown!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.54,0:17:26.14,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Why didn’t you awaken me earlier?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.83,0:17:31.55,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Sir! I was concerned about your health,\Nso I delayed the report.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.55,0:17:34.06,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Please punish me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.58,0:17:35.96,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That’s not fair, Kotsubaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.96,0:17:37.67,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Captain, please punish me, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.67,0:17:40.15,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Don’t copy what I say, Kiyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.15,0:17:41.80,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I’m not copying you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.80,0:17:42.80,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That’s enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.89,0:17:47.65,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,In any case…\NI can’t stay here like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.42,0:17:56.99,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That’s…Squad Six Captain,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.40,0:17:59.21,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Byakuya Kuchiki!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.59,0:18:03.27,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Byakuya Kuchiki…\NH-He’s…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.27,0:18:04.65,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You know him?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.62,0:18:08.03,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.32,0:18:11.45,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The Kuchiki clan is one\Nof the four noble houses
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.45,0:18:13.34,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,with the highest rank.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.75,0:18:16.31,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That guy’s the current clan leader.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.13,0:18:21.62,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Of the thirteen captains today,\Nhe’s probably the most famous.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.41,0:18:24.09,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,This is the worst thing\Nthat could happen…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.09,0:18:26.13,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Someone like him appearing\Nat a time like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.30,0:18:29.84,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It’s no good.\NThere’s no way we could win.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.40,0:18:36.66,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe we should just beg for our lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.55,0:18:41.50,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,W-What are you saying, Ganju?!\NLet’s run away with Rukia!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.50,0:18:44.63,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You idiot! Do you see any way out?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.09,0:18:47.09,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,This bridge is the only way!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.69,0:18:53.04,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Are you telling me\Nto risk my life for her?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.62,0:18:56.04,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,She killed my brother, you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.04,0:18:57.71,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,For someone…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.39,0:19:00.48,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,For someone like her?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.43,0:19:08.64,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.86,0:19:11.43,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I guess it can’t be helped.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.88,0:19:16.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,There was never any reason\Nfor you to save Rukia, to begin with.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.63,0:19:21.59,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It would be asking too much\Nto force you to stay here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.52,0:19:25.01,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,So, at least when you escape\Nfrom here,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.01,0:19:26.81,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,please take Rukia with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.70,0:19:32.57,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I’ll make a stand here,\Nand hold him off.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.88,0:19:35.60,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,W-What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.80,0:19:39.36,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I think I understand how you feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.36,0:19:42.25,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,No one would give his life\Nto save his enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.25,0:19:43.60,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That’s got nothing to do with it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.82,0:19:46.10,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You felt the Spiritual Pressure,\Ndidn’t you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.10,0:19:47.30,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,No way can we handle this.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.30,0:19:48.46,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I know that, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.77,0:19:53.66,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Still, I came this far because\NI wanted to save Rukia.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.45,0:19:58.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I can’t just leave\Nwithout doing anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.22,0:20:01.84,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for everything you’ve done!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.47,0:20:03.58,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I’ll be on my way.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.42,0:20:12.90,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Don’t do it, Hanataro! You can’t…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.96,0:20:15.88,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing? Let me through!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.57,0:20:20.86,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.70,0:20:25.00,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What does he think he can do\Nwithout even a Zanpaku-to?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.12,0:20:27.92,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,He’s trembling…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.85,0:20:31.71,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You’re just a weakling.\NDon’t go acting so tough!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.67,0:20:33.61,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.58,0:20:36.18,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.26,0:20:46.43,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Stay back!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.43,0:20:47.62,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ganju…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.13,0:20:53.23,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Not…again!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.80,0:21:03.14,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, Brother.\NAvenging you will have to wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.26,0:21:05.59,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,If you’re gonna blame anyone,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.59,0:21:11.55,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,blame Sis for not raising me to be\Na coward who would run out on his friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.77,0:21:15.40,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Here I come, young ‘un!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.10,0:21:18.86,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I am your opponent!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.16,0:21:30.93,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Happy people
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.93,0:21:32.70,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, come on, come on
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.54,0:21:35.44,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Happy people
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.06,0:21:37.34,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Here we go!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.34,0:21:43.21,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Everybody stand up! Everybody fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.18,0:21:48.80,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Within your heart, you may feel uneasy
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.80,0:21:52.71,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But keep your head right up!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.56,0:21:54.72,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,To the sky!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.85,0:21:56.89,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,No matter when (Oh yeah!)
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.89,0:21:59.08,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,No matter where (Oh yeah!)
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.08,0:22:01.50,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Just call me anytime! (Oh yeah!)
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.50,0:22:03.70,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I’ll be here for you
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.70,0:22:07.68,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Happy people in the house!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.98,0:22:10.92,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,With a tough smile
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.02,0:22:16.34,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Happy people in the house!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.55,0:22:19.25,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Let’s live!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.17,0:22:21.04,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Wow
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.57,0:22:23.62,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Happy people in the house
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.50,0:22:25.68,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,All right
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.91,0:22:27.72,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Happy people
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.33,0:22:34.56,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The story is finally\Nreaching a climax.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.56,0:22:37.26,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe it's time for me\Nto reveal my secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.26,0:22:39.19,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Can you guess what my secret is?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.20,0:22:41.37,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You can speak human, but not cat!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.37,0:22:43.31,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You dye your fur black!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.31,0:22:44.28,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You're actually a dog!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.28,0:22:46.84,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Bingo! Listen, you trying to\Nmake a fool of me?!